<br>
Also I apologize to anyone who feels I am "gimping" the encounter by preparing for it in advance. I simply wish to be most prepared for it. I will gather whatever info I can and then go for it. If you do not wish to divulge such information because you feel cheated, I respect that. If you do care to help, I appreciate that.<br>
